title: 69th parallel south
text:
The 69th parallel south is a <a href="circle%20of%20latitude">circle of latitude</a> that is 69 <a href="degree%20%28angle%29">degrees</a> <a href="south">south</a> of the <a href="Earth">Earth's</a> <a href="equator">equatorial plane</a>, in the <a href="Antarctic">Antarctic</a>. It crosses the <a href="Southern%20Ocean">Southern Ocean</a> and <a href="Antarctica">Antarctica</a>.
Around the world.
